Greek Yogurt Waffles

25 min
$5
250 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

glutendairyegg

Dietary Tags:

vegetarianhigh-protein

Cuisine:

American

Course:

breakfast

breakfasteasybrunch

Description

Fluffy and protein-packed waffles that are perfect for breakfast or brunch.

Ingredients

  • all-purpose flour: 1 cup
  • greek yogurt: 1 cup
  • milk: 1/2 cup
  • egg: 1
  • baking powder: 2 tsp
  • sugar: 2 tbsp
  • vanilla extract: 1 tsp
  • butter (melted): 2 tbsp
